y create a strong competitor to Red Hat, the impact of the latter is self-evident. As a result, Red Hat Linux\'s dominant position, most likely not be maintained. <br /> Another way of saying that the possible acquisition of SUSE Linux is IBM. IBM and Red Hat have many years of cooperation, if IBM is determined to acquire SuSE, whether it will continue to maintain this relationship depends on how IBM SuSE have a bit of hope. May in any case, once the IBM acquisition of SuSE, in the next few years will pose a threat to Red Hat, although a direct financial impact will not be more than 60 million per year. <br /> More worse, IBM has used the line software and hardware product lines. IBM back in 2000 to drop it into the billions of dollars to support Linux, and now all of its product line can be no barrier into Linux. Once the full support of some kind of IBM Linux, its influence is limitless. <br /> There is also a view that he may come forward to buy Red Hat, SUSE Linux. However, because Red Hat and SUSE high degree of overlap of business and the acquisition would mean in the next 5 to 7 years, have to bear the financial support of SuSE. Therefore, the Red Hat acquisition is unlikely. But only this possibility is the Red Hat Linux to consolidate its industry in the boss position. The combination of SUSE and Red Hat, but also may give the next part of the brand of Linux to the market space. <br /> Indeed, the rise of Linux has by no means the brand is not possible. September 21, Oracle\'s global technology and application of the General Assembly, Oracle announced that Oracle software and hardware to optimize the introduction of a fast, modern and reliable enterprise-class Oracle Unbreakable Linux kernel core. Within the Oracle software and hardware industrial chain has improved steadily after, Oracle Unbreakable Linux is playing an increasingly larger stage. And industry experts generally believe that Oracle\'s acquisition of VMware far less likely to have large, and Oracle\'s acquisition will not cause too much of the current market share. <br /> Thus, with the approaching date of acquisition SUSE Linux, Red Hat\'s leadership position may not be preserved, Oracle Unbreakable Linux is constantly looking for the opportunity to host. The most elusive is the SUSE Linux, it decided to change the industry, but also to sway their own destiny to become uncertain. Regardless of where to change, Linux industry may be at the eve of regime change.</span></span> </p> (Editor: South African Ant) </td></tr></table>'),(234,'linux','en','/a/os/linux/2010/0507/98.html','New book &quot;Linux the essence of enterprise applications,&quot; being finalized, release all','2010-05-07','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<font color=\"red\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">Ã£Â€ÂReproduced in the form of a hyperlink when you identify the source and author information in the article and the statementÃ£Â€Â‘ <br /> Original Link:</span></span></font> <script> \r\nfunction selecturl(){ \r\nz=document.body.createTextRange(); \r\nz.moveToElementText(selecturlDiv); \r\nz.select(); \r\n} \r\n</script><script>document.write(location.href)</script><table width=\"100%\"><tr><td><p> Blink of an eye, &quot;step by step Linux&quot; has been published six months, and in the process, received a lot of letters from readers and counseling, including encouragement have different opinions, but certainly the majority, to get everyone\'s approval and support, I am very pleased, thank you for the encouragement and support consistent, because this is just the beginning, I believe I can do better! </p><p> &quot;Step by step Linux&quot; has been reprinted once, fixed some errors in the first edition, once again thank the support of readers, of which 60% of the amendments when the feedback from readers is very grateful to these loyal readers, your support is I wrote this book the greatest power! </p><p> In the &quot;step by step Linux&quot; published after 